WILL OSPREAY def. LANCE ARCHER

Great match, no surprise there. We need Lance Archer in a significant storyline that progresses him as a character.

MJF attacks Ospreay after the match. Kyle Fletcher runs out to save Will Ospreay from the beat down, against Don Callis’ wishes.

Fletcher grabs a mic and challenges MJF to a match next week.

